data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value:
SELECT tblRenewal.ID, tblRenewal.FCardNo, tblRenewal.Date, tblRenewal.RenewalYear, tblRenewal.Fee, tblRenewal.PoorFund, tblRenewal.LateFee, tblRenewal.Total, tblRenewal.Link_Account, tblRenewal.CardFee, tblRenewal.AdultMembers, tblRenewal.TotalMembers, tblRenewal.ReceiptNo, tblAccounts.AccountName, tblFamilyMember.MemberName AS Head, tblFamilyMember.FatherName AS FName, tblFamily.[Sign] AS Orakh, tblRenewal.RenewalTo, IsNull([EducationFund],0.00) As EducationFund ,IsNull([KabristanFund],0.00) As KabristanFund ,IsNull([ZakatFund],0.00) As ZakatFund ,IsNull([DonationFund],0.00) As DonationFund ,IsNull([TamiratiFund],0.00) As TamiratiFund ,(Select count(FamilyMemberID) from tblfamilymember where fcardno=@FCardNO and AgeGroup='Minor' and Gender='Male' AND Active = 1) as TotalMaleMinor ,(Select count(FamilyMemberID) from tblfamilymember where fcardno=@FCardNO and AgeGroup='Minor' and Gender='Female' AND Active = 1) as TotalFemaleMinor ,(Select count(FamilyMemberID) from tblfamilymember where fcardno=@FCardNO and AgeGroup='Adult' and Gender='Female' AND Active = 1) as TotalFemaleAdult ,(Select count(FamilyMemberID) from tblfamilymember LEFT OUTER JOIN tblNIC on tblFamilyMember.FamilyMemberID = tblNIC.MemberID where tblfamilymember.fcardno=@FCardNO and tblFamilyMember.AgeGroup='Adult' and tblFamilyMember.Gender='Male' AND tblFamilyMember.Active = 1 AND tblNIC.IsNICPrinted IS NULL) as CIDC
FROM tblRenewal INNER JOIN tblAccounts ON tblRenewal.Account = tblAccounts.ID INNER JOIN tblFamilyMember ON tblFamilyMember.FCardNo = tblRenewal.FCardNo INNER JOIN tblFamily ON tblFamilyMember.FCardNo = tblFamily.FCardNo
WHERE tblFamilyMember.LeaderRelation = 'Head of Family' AND ReceiptNo = @ReceiptNo

data.name: txtFemaleQuery.Text
data.value: SELECT tblFamilyMember.AgeGroup as GroupType, count(tblFamilyMember.AgeGroup) as AgeGroup FROM tblFamilyMember WHERE FCardNo = @FCardNo and tblFamilyMember.Active = 1 and tblFamilyMember.Gender = 'Female' Group by AgeGroup Order by GroupType
